<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282736>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 33. Male stridulatory file and male abdominal apex: 17, 22 – 26. Sinochlora apicalis sp. nov.; 18. S. semicircula; 19, 27 – 30. S. longipenis sp. nov.; 20, 31 – 33. S. cucullata sp. nov.; 21. S. stylosa. 17 – 21. stridulatory file; 22, 27, 31. abdominal apex in lateral view; 23, 28, 32. tenth abdominal tergum in dorsal view; 26, 30, 33. subgenital plate in ventral view; 24. right cercus in lateral view; 25. epiproct in apical view; 29. apex of epiproct in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282736/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282738>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46 – 68. Male abdominal apex and female subgenital plate: 46 – 47, 67. Sinochlora stylosa; 48. S. trispinosa; 49 – 51. S. apicalis sp. nov.; 52 – 54. S. longipenis sp. nov.; 55 – 56, 65. S. cucullata sp. nov.; 57. S. longifissa; 58. S. aequalis; 59. S. tibetensis; 60, 68. S. trapezialis; 61. S. sinensis; 62. S. szechwanensis; 63. S. nonspinosa; 64, 66. S. semicircula. 46, 48 – 49, 52, 55, 57 – 64. male abdominal apex in lateral view; 50, 53. male epiproct in lateral view; 47, 51, 54, 56. male tenth abdominal tergum in dorsal view; 65 – 68. female subgenital plate in ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282738/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

